name: Zhao Jinmai (Chinese actress)
description:
These girls next door have grown up. Keep moving on.

~~

It's confusing again and again that after I set training images larger to 512*768 & 768*768, I thought I would get better results, but the outputs after hirex.fix (448*640-->716*1024, denoising 0.45, ESRgan4x) look not like her, sometimes even worse.

~~

Refer to my png info.

Weighted around 0.5-0.75 (up to your model).

~~

Be kind to these lovely.

Legal & Risk
